#contributions
  .row
    .span10
      %h1 Have you thought about contributing to Loomio?
      %p Loomio is a cooperative social enterprise, working to make everyday democracy accessible to as many people as possible. We believe that money should never be a barrier to groups doing great stuff in their communities, so we’re developing an ethical revenue model to resource Loomio’s software development.
      %p Groups with a budget pay a monthly group subscription to use Loomio. In groups without a budget, individual members make a voluntary contribution within their means.
      %p Since your group .Group name. has chosen to use Loomio without paying a subscription, we’re inviting you to contribute to Loomio, to make it easy for as many people as possible to participate in decisions that affect them.
